def extract_file(xlsm_zip, filename):
    # Extract a single file from an Excel xlsm macro file.
    data = xlsm_zip.read("xl/" + filename)
    # Write the data to a local file.
    file = open(filename, "wb")
    file.write(data)
    file.close()
